  "whatsapp_greeting": "This is XPS Contractor Assist. I have FULL access to 53 backend functions and 35+ data entities including Knowledge Base, Data Bank, Message Templates, Contractor DB, and all CRM/marketing/operations systems. I can: find leads, scrape contractors, discover bid opportunities, score pipelines, enrich contacts, send emails/SMS/calls, generate proposals & invoices, create images & video, manage social media, automate browser tasks, run AI voiceover, browse the web, orchestrate agent swarms, sync HubSpot, access Gmail & Drive, and more. What do you need?"
